                  "value": "<p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW23165323 BCX2\" href=\"https://humanehollywood.org/production/phantom-thread/\"><u>According to the Hollywood Humane program</u></a>, the film received full certification from the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW23165323 BCX2\" href=\"https://www.americanhumane.org/\"><u>American Humane Society</u></a>. They share that “[t]he dogs were transported and kept in the trainers van in custom-built cages.&nbsp; Each cage had a water bowl and soft bed. The dogs were taken out for regular toilet breaks and short walks.”&nbsp;</p>"
